=================================================
Thank you for downloading web-spa!
=================================================

This program is a web knocking implementation
that allows a single HTTP/S request to authorise 
an O/S command to be executed. 

Please also see the README file for further 
information.

=================================================
INSTALL: Table of contents
=================================================

- Prerequisites for web-spa

=================================================
- Prerequisites for web-spa
=================================================

The following programs must be installed in order
for web-spa to run:

- Java 1.6 or later
  
Java can be downloaded at 
http://www.java.com/en/download/

You only need to download and install the "Java 
Runtime Environment (JRE)".

For development and contributing to the code base
of web-spa, you will require the "Java 
Development Kit (JDK)".
=================================================
